About US
We are bringing leading-edge, easy to use analytics to Non-Profits, Academic Institutions and Political Organizations. We help fundraisers, while working with existing software, create new ways to identify, target, and engage their networks. 
We need energetic individuals seeking to transform technical ability into leadership roles, and as a pre-series A company, we're looking for the best professionals to help develop our team and culture. We offer a flexible work environment and highly competitive equity package to qualified candidates. If you're interested in early stage opportunities to accelerate your tech career in the non-profit, academic, and political sectors, We are the perfect startup for you. 
